projectType: AI Powered Health Assistant Mobile App
projectDescription: Developed a cross-platform health management application featuring secure user authentication, medication reminders, and adherence tracking that improved consistency by 35% using a notification tracking system. Implemented appointment scheduling and emergency contact management. Integrated AI-driven health insights and medicine information retrieval using the Google Gemini API to enhance personalized user experience. Delivered an intuitive, real-time synchronized mobile app optimized for Android.
techStack: React Native, Kotlin, Expo Framework, Firebase Authentication, Firestore Database
